data.description:
Welcome to your charming new home in the heart of Chaffee Park! This adorable 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. New carpeting throughout. The detached garage offers both convenience and additional storage options, while the spacious fenced-in yard provides a secure and private oasis for you and your loved ones. Imagine weekend barbecues or simply enjoying the outdoors in your very own expansive yard. Located in a vibrant neighborhood, this home is just a stone's throw away from shopping and dining options, ensuring that you're never far from the essentials. Explore nearby trails for invigorating walks or bike rides, and relish the proximity to Berkeley Park, offering a perfect spot for picnics and outdoor activities.
Commute with ease, thanks to the property's quick access to both I-70 and I-25. Whether you're heading downtown or exploring the wider Denver area, you'll appreciate the convenience of these major highways.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this adorable home yours. Embrace the warmth, convenience, and charm that await you in this delightful Chaffee Park residence. Schedule your showing today and experience the joy of calling this place home!
